To add ad credits to your account, you'll need to ensure that your account has completed and passed business verification. Additionally, your account or campaign must have accumulated over $5,000 in spend. Once these conditions are met, you can establish a relationship with an Account Manager who can request the ad credit functionality to be enabled for you.
